menu "Animation Decoder"

    config ANIMATION_DECODER_STATIC_FRAME_DELAY_MS
        int "Static image frame delay (ms)"
        default 100
        range 10 1000
        help
            Frame delay used for static images (PNG, JPEG) when played as animations.
            This controls how long a static image is displayed before the decoder
            indicates it's ready to "advance" to the next frame (which is the same image).

endmenu

